Name: Daily
Description: done, produced, or occurring every day or every weekday; every day

Name: Daily-even
Description: recurring (~4 hour) period of a day cycle: 2pm to 6pm (sunset)

Name: Daily-morn
Description: recurring (~4 hour) period of a day cycle: sunrise (6am) to 10am

Name: Daily-night
Description: recurring (~12 hour) period of a day cycle: 6pm to 6am (sunrise)

Name: Daily-noon
Description: recurring (~4 hour) period of a day cycle: (midday) 10am to 2pm

Name: Fall/Autumn
Description: 9/21 thru 12/20 of the annual calendar year

Name: Hourly
Description: done or occurring every hour; by the hour.

Name: Monthly
Description: done, produced, or occurring every month or every monthday; every month

Name: PeriodOfRec
Description: Period of Record - contains all of the data ever taken

Name: Quarterly
Description: done, produced, or occurring once every quarter of a year; events occuring four times a year

Name: Seasonal
Description: relating to or characteristic of a particular season of the year

Name: Spring
Description: 3/21 thru 6/20 of the annual calendar year

Name: Summer
Description: 6/21 thru 9/20 of the annual calendar year

Name: Ultimate
Description: being or happening at the end of a process; final; a final or fundamental fact or principle

Name: Weekly
Description: done, produced, or occurring once a week; periodical issued every week.

Name: Winter
Description: 12/21 thru 3/20 of the annual calendar year

Name: Yearly
Description: done, produced, or occurring every year or every year; annual event
